title: 23/10/2015 - Council wins two National Social Work Awards (Pembrokeshire County Council)
text: ( Source : Pembrokeshire County Council ) Pembrokeshire County Council has won two national awards. The Authority 's Children 's Services were successful in the sixth annual British Association of Social Workers ( BASW ) Cymru Social Work Awards
